<a id="about"></a>
<h2>About Me</h2>
<p>I'm Felipe José Bravo Márquez, I was born in 3th January 1984 on Santiago, Chile. I am currently studying a PhD in computer science at the <a href="http://www.waikato.ac.nz/" >University of Waikato</a> in the <a href="http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/ml/">Machine Learning Group</a>. My supervisors are professors <a href="http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/~bernhard/">Bernhard Pfahringer</a> and <a href="http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/~eibe/">Eibe Frank</a>. </p>

<p>
 In my research thesis I investigate algorithms for domain-focused sentiment analysis in time-evolving social media streams.
</p>

<p>
</p>

</div>


